ore":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5O14yr.gif&amp;h=2ca4ff17&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n果日打人好撚勇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲拎包煙出黎食"},{"pid":"a05193952790a1a112f7af775c186d27bfc2c38b","tid":2417811,"uid":26014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:51:19.000Z","msg":"自己走入去撩事鬥飛，事後又扮受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a8245ef06f3a8c5f216e0f1b3ffa284e73a3bd","tid":2417811,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02c96df1fb240cb0adfab007f4acdbcdfc39fa6","tid":2417811,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"36a8245ef06f3a8c5f216e0f1b3ffa284e73a3bd","tid":2417811,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:58:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13838&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=010cb4ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13838</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第七庭 <br />\n#練錦鴻法官 #審訊 [1/5]<br />\nD1: 黃(31), D2: 吳(23)<br />\nD3: 蘇(24) #0707旺角<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1) 猥褻侵犯另一人 [D1]<br />\n黃手足被控於2019年7月7日在九龍旺角山東街與西洋菜南街交界，猥褻侵犯女子X。<br />\n<br />\n(2) 非法禁錮 [全部被告]<br />\n(3) 非法集結 [全部被告]<br />\n<br />\n承上：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13818&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=d21f8119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13818</a><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n下午PW1女子X繼續作供並接受盤問。代表首被告的姚本成大律師指出X在整個過程中不斷大叫救命、打劫，但只叫過一次強姦，而且從片段所見，她被白衣男子掂到時亦無嗌非禮，在上警車前都無向警員講自己被非禮，甚至上到警車後有女警問有咩事發生，亦無提及被人非禮。<br />\n<br />\n當晚女警見女子X沒有被毆打，身體無大礙，建議X先回家休息。X的母親翌日致電X稱在電視見到佢，X因事件被廣泛報導感到不安，於是下午去報警。<br />\n<br />\n代表首被告的姚本成大律師質疑，X報警只是因為被報導，而非被非禮。X否認上述講法。<br />\n<br />\nbtw，<strong><span class=\"red\">女子X在2021年1月因飲醉酒而打傷休班女警(X的舊同學)，被控襲擊至造成身體傷害罪成，被判18個月感化令 [判刑原則有錯，明顯過輕？] 。到2月又因違反檢疫令被判14日監禁&hellip;&hellip;審訊明續</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n💛感謝臨時直播員💛"},{"pid":"9837cc8ffd79768018dcd577c41cd308c6b46260","tid":2417811,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:05:21.000Z","msg":"佢唔喺現場咪無事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5c44a9683aef134499668e5ab1e6074df8ce63","tid":2417811,"uid":8830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}